ft score:   {uplift_slearner.min():.4f}\")\n","print(f\"\\nCustomers with NEGATIVE uplift (Sleeping Dogs): \"\n","      f\"{(uplift_slearner < 0).sum()}\")\n","print(f\"Customers with POSITIVE uplift (Persuadables):  \"\n","      f\"{(uplift_slearner > 0).sum()}\")\n","\n","print(\"\"\"\n","T-LEARNER vs S-LEARNER:\n","→ T-Learner trains separate models — captures treatment heterogeneity better\n","→ S-Learner uses treatment as feature — may underweight treatment signal\n","→ T-Learner generally preferred for marketing uplift problems\n","\"\"\")"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":12,"id":"f5059afa","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2026-05-13T08:48:20.670637Z","iopub.status.busy":"2026-05-13T08:48:20.670282Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-05-13T08:48:21.15919Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-05-13T08:48:21.157802Z"},"papermill":{"duration":0.500576,"end_time":"2026-05-13T08:48:21.161503+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-05-13T08:48:20.660927+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"outputs":[{"data":{"image/png":"\n","text/plain":["<Figure size 1400x500 with 2 Axes>"]},"metadata":{},"output_type":"display_data"},{"name":"stdout","output_type":"stream","text":["Customer type distribution (T-Learner):\n","CustomerType\n","Lost Cause          6899\n","Low Persuadable     1355\n","High Persuadable     181\n","Sleeping Dog         104\n","Name: count, dtype: int64\n"]}],"source":["fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 5))\n","\n","# T-Learner uplift distribution\n","axes[0].hist(uplift_tlearner, bins=50, color='steelblue', \n","             edgecolor='black', alpha=0.7)\n","axes[0].axvline(0, color='red', linestyle='--', linewidth=2,\n","                label='Zero uplift line')\n","axes[0].set_title('T-Learner Uplift Score Distribution', fontweight='bold')\n","axes[0].set_xlabel('Uplift Score')\n","axes[0].set_ylabel('Count')\n","axes[0].legend()\n","\n","# S-Learner uplift distribution\n","axes[1].hist(uplift_slearner, bins=50, color='tomat